                            <comment id="13009348" author="arikkfir" created="Mon, 21 Mar 2011 20:17:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m usually rooting to change incorrect behavior, but to keep backward compabilitiy, I think this property should be deprecated and a new one should be introduced which enforces the correct behavior (overriding this property if both are specified).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
